#Title
Alphabetic sorting ignores country

#Environment
Pixel 3a, Android 9
Environment independent

#Steps to reproduce
1. Run the application
2. Wait until cities list is loaded
3. Type 'porto' into search field
4. Wait until search result is ready
5. Check cities order

#Expected Result
Cities list is alphabetically order with considering name and country

#Actual Result
Cities list is alphabetically order only with considering name

#Severity/Priority
Medium/Medium

#Notes
The defect cause may be City class compareTo method realization.